      <p>
        Virtual Vacation Zone+ is an interactive poetic memoir, board game, and
        visual novel. Submit your own vacation memory before you embark on your
        own cerebral getaway. Play a simple board game to determine what
        emotions you feel next on your vacation, and maybe even read other
        players&rsquo; vacation memories.
      </p>
      <p>
        Halfway through the game, you can play the subgame
        <strong><q>Telemetry &amp; Jeff,</q></strong> a short visual novel about
        Telemetry trying to find herself some lunch.
      </p>
      <p>
        You can play the game on
        <a href="https://meisekimiu.itch.io/virtual-vacation-zone">Itch.io</a>
        right now! Feel free to submit your own memories!
      </p>
